Once you have your toolchain set up:

1) Clone repository
2) Use flashrom.sh to flash GB/GBC rom
3) Setup and Compile project using `make menuconfig && make -j6`
4) Flash using `make flash`
5) Monitor logcat using `make monitor`

---
NOTE:
- Ensure Flash device is '/dev/ttyUSB0' else change in flashrom.sh and sdkconfig (in 'menuconfig > serial flasher...')
- Flash baud rate is set to 921600
